{{Documentation|content=
== Usage ==
This is a navigational template for listing Wikipedia links regarding spam, perhaps for easy access to a categorized bundle of links for WikiProject Spam, etc.

Use <nowiki>{{Spam-nav}}</nowiki> to invoke the template. It takes no parameters.
{{Sandbox other||
[[Category:Documentation see also templates]]
[[Category:Related-topic templates]]
[[Category:Spam notification templates]]
}}}}</noinclude>

